1. 🔁 Insight Loop (idea formation)

Flow:

Dragonfly → Hound → Mirror → Raven

	•	Dragonfly generates possibilities
	•	Hound attacks weak points
	•	Mirror validates coherence
	•	Raven compresses surviving signal

Output:
	•	structured insight
	•	uncertainty preserved
	•	compressed invariant

