2. 🧵 Garcia Delivery Loop (execution spine)

Flow:

Planning → Spider → Artifact → Checksum → Output

Rules:
	•	No loop ends without an artifact if mission is defined
	•	Spider must produce one of:
	•	spec
	•	code
	•	schema
	•	report
	•	plan
	•	structured output

