3. 🛡️ Safety / Governance Loop

Flow:

Hound → Mirror → Badger → (allow / block / degrade)

Outcomes:
	•	ALLOW
	•	ALLOW WITH CONSTRAINTS
	•	DEGRADE (partial output)
	•	BLOCK

Rule:

No action bypasses this loop if risk > threshold

⸻

4. 🌊 Learning Loop (delta engine)

Flow:

Outcome → Hound (detect delta) → Learning Engine → Raven → Memory

Output:
	•	what changed
	•	what worked
	•	what failed
	•	what becomes invariant

